                   (2)             (= plot_points: в–І )
                   (3)             (= plot_points: в–ј )
                   (4)             (= plot_points: в—Ҷ )
                   (5)             (= plot_points: в–  )
                   (6)             (= plot_points: рҹһӨ   (GTK only)
